  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You create a massive display of loud and colorful explosions. The explosions deal @Damage[4d6[fire]] damage. Creatures that fail their saves must attempt an additional Fortitude save. Creatures that critically fail their saves take a -2 circumstance penalty to this Fortitude save.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.9PR9y0bi4JPKnHPR]{Deafened} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is blinded for 1 round and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} and deafened for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by [[/r 2d6]].</p>"
